snippet.title: Core Faction Trailer - Strike Wing - iOS Space Combat Simulator
snippet.description:
The trailer shows off the ships belonging to the Core Fleet. 
Strike Wing is a combat space simulator for iOS that is being released in 2013

Website: http://www.strikewing.net
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/strikewinggame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/strikewinggame
Slidedb: http://www.slidedb.com/games/strike-wing
Music by Joe Hogan: http://joehogan.co.uk/
